
Main class - Client
Unit Test class - ClientUnitTest

Start the Concourse Server and run the applications for see the output.

Functionalities:

Unique Username along with password,emailId, countryName to register.  
UserName and password should match to login after registering.
List all user details registered in database. 
Clear all user details.
User can login,unregister and remove themselves from DB.

Validity check:

Validity check for email.
Password should be atleast 6 characters.
Usename should be unique to register.
username password should match for login.
